Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.88,0:00:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,《纸牌屋》前情提要...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Previously on House of Cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.68,0:00:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你别想靠恐吓回到决策桌上  雷蒙德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You cannot bully your way back to the table, Raymond,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.39,0:00:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你也休想收买国会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just as you cannot buy the keys to Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.80,0:00:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你成功维持众议院多数席位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Best of luck keeping your majority in the House.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.68,0:00:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,她在纽约\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's in New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.85,0:00:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-是亚当·嘉乐威吗    -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Adam Galloway?   - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.27,0:00:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你为亚当·嘉乐威工作  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I understand you work for Adam Galloway.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.98,0:00:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 能挣些生活费\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. It's a way to pay the bills.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.81,0:00:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那为什么我两天找到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So how is it that I've found more in two days
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.56,0:00:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,比你两个月查到的还多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}than you have in two months?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.65,0:00:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-你就是只寄生虫    -你一样  丹顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You're a parasite.   - So are you, Danton.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.94,0:00:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你赢过多少次选举\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How many elections have you won?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.24,0:00:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你的办公桌在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look where your desk is now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.45,0:00:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们就互不相欠了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'd say we're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.95,0:00:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我的副总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not my Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.79,0:00:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但他是个危险的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But he's a dangerous man.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.87,0:00:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也可以很危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can be dangerous, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.37,0:00:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的风险有多大  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How much danger are we in, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.37,0:00:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们现在就结束谈话  就没有风险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}None, if we end this conversation right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.38,0:00:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你赢过多少次选举\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you ever loved anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.42,0:00:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我很高兴我拥有现在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm glad I have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.96,0:00:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,报道出来以后生意一下兴隆了不少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, there's been a big bump in business since it came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.05,0:00:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,街上排起大队\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm talking lines around the block.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.92,0:00:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们用弗莱迪烧烤连锁店撑起这个名声\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's fill up that map with Freddy's Barbecue Joints.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.05,0:00:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你终止和塔斯克的合作关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You kill your co-venture with Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.76,0:00:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们当初可没说到这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That was never part of the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.97,0:00:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们别无选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're running out of options.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.14,0:00:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你的冰山一角正在融化  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The tip of your iceberg is melting, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.42,0:00:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}床单下的安德伍德夫人  和摄影家亚当·嘉乐威的私情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.60,0:02:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-你好啊  弗莱迪  最近怎样    -挺好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey, Freddy! How ya doing?   - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.54,0:02:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好  你这么说我就安心了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, that's what I like to hear.
