Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,日报我能联系的人都联系了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I spoke to everyone I know at the Daily.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.84,0:04:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,没人告诉我谁给的照片  但肯定是雷米\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nobody's naming sources, but it has to be Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嘉乐威要出面回应吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is Galloway going on the record?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.86,0:04:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不会的  他会先和我们接触\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He wouldn't. Not without speaking to us first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.03,0:04:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-最好确保这一点    -我这就去和亚当说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Let's be sure about that.   - I'll talk to Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.28,0:04:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,也许避免和他接触会更好些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe it's smarter to avoid contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.89,0:04:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,总得有人出面回应\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Somebody has to respond,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.20,0:05:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不是他就是我们  或者一起回应\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}whether it's him, or us, or both.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得协调好  小心应对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have to coordinate, and do it carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.79,0:05:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这事交给我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.87,0:05:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们先想好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, let's just think this through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.55,0:05:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不会有问题的  弗兰西斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've got it covered, Francis.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我该怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.47,0:05:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,还去办公室吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Head back to the office?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.47,0:05:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你还是在家办公比较好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think you should work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你出门的话  很难躲开媒体\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't avoid the press if you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.88,0:05:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-那好  你把好门    -好的  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- All right. You hold down the fort.   - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你听克莱尔差遣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you follow Claire's lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.93,0:05:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这事会解决的  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll shut this down, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,绝不能让人质疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There can't be any doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们再过一遍时间线\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's walk through a timeline.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-你首次见他是什么时候    -惠特尼双年展\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So you first met him when? -In Whitney Biennial...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这事伤害了我们两个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This hurts us both.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但要着手去处理的人不是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it's not my wound to suture.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.71,0:05:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,克莱尔必须亲自动手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Claire must be the surgeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,只有她才能稳住局势\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only she can stop the bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,里面有盘子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know we got them plates in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,按你要求的改好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All the changes you asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,多给你5%的追补股份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gave you five more points on the post-recoupment share.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,营销宣传材料需要你认可\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Approval over all the marketing materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,银泉旗舰店的人事也要经你认可\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Approval over the staff hires of the flagship in Silver Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-接下来做什么    -签字就行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So, what next?   - You sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-然后我九万五就到手了    -这周末吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And I get my $95,000?   - By the end of the week.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.15,0:05:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,得先把钱从主账户注入公司账户\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just have to wire it from our main account into the LLC,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:05:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,还得核对账目\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}had cash years to check for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.86,0:06:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我还想给你看看这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to show you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这是酱料瓶的样品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a mockup of the bottle design.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他们已经开始为银泉店的外观\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we already started on the concept layouts
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,进行概念设计了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for the Silver Spring location.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么墙毡都裂开了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why's that linoleum peeling up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.92,0:06:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,追求真实感啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To make it seem real.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望比这漂亮些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanted it to look nicer than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以改掉墙毡的设计\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can scratch the peeling linoleum,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.34,0:06:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但不想显得太高端\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we don't want it to look too nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.62,0:06:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让白人有种体验下层生活的感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want them white folks to feel like they slummin' it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不  是为了营造地道的气氛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, to have an authentic atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我就负责扮演黑鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I get to play the nigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,弗莱迪  你也知道这种事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, Freddy, you know how this works.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.07,0:06:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不只是来吃肋排\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They don't just want the ribs,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.17,0:06:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,而是要那种体验\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they want the experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.42,0:06:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,还不用出市郊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but without having to leave the suburbs for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们又不是卖烛光晚餐的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're not selling candlelit dinners here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.35,0:06:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但我保证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I promise,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所有决策都会经过你的首肯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}nothing gets built without your signing off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:06:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让我怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, what do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:07:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-我要你出面否认    -否认恋情吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I need you to deny it.   - The affair?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,恋情  照片  所有这一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The affair, taking the photograph, everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有公开来往的记录\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have a public history.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾捐献作品给...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I donated work for your...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.88,0:07:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以说那纯粹是业务往来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can say we had a business relationship,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但你没有给我拍躺在床上的照片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but that you didn't take the picture of me in the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,就说是合成的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was Photoshopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,随便你怎么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever it is you need to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉  克莱尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm so sorry, Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.68,0:07:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我只印了一版  还在我这儿呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I only have one print and it's still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那个你也得销毁掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have to destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,电脑存档也要删掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The digital file also.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但删之前先发给我们一份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But e-mail us a copy first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.69,0:07:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得确认照片里没有任何痕迹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to make sure that there's nothing in the image
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,能联系到你的工作室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that links to your studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,全都听你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever you think is best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  亚当\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时在看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I watched you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.80,0:07:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你接受CNN直播采访的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...when you did the CNN interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.93,0:07:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来打定主意不看的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I promised myself I wouldn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.29,0:07:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但我忍不住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I couldn't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要因为这种事才说上话真是遗憾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a shame it takes this for us to talk to one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:07:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,除了这事  你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're well, besides this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.86,0:08:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  你来过之后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. I spent three months in Colombia
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.13,0:08:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我去哥伦比亚工作了三个月\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}after you came up here to work,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,其实也是逃避\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but also to get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.16,0:08:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我遇到了一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I met someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.97,0:08:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,她来自波哥大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's from Bogotá.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,与当地非政府组织合作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She was working with an NGO there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,叫伊奈兹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her name's Inez.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们同居了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's living with me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,进展很快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Things happened quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.11,0:08:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  确实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. They did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我该挂了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.58,0:08:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,得到指示前  我不能和媒体接触\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So I won't talk to the press until I get instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,能听到你的声音真好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's good to hear your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-打完电话了    -嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You finished?   - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真是疯狂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Crazy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.71,0:09:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,海洛因  可卡因  霹雳可卡因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Smack, crack, blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.46,0:09:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不用  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,来点吧  老头  我们手里应有尽有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, old man. We got what you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都不需要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,想要进门  就得买点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gotta buy somethin' if you want to get inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,别挡路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get out the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.36,0:09:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我认真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For real.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈的给我滚开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You need to get the fuck on outta my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.06,0:09:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你闹着玩而已  黑鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just fucking with you, nigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.18,0:09:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈的冷静点嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Chill the fuck out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.33,0:09:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:10:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你爷爷  开门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your grandfather. Open up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.36,0:10:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's your plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.27,0:10:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,在家办公\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Work from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就不会把闹剧带去白宫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't need me dragging this circus to the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.93,0:10:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说声明打算怎么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean in terms of a statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在起草  力求简短有力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're drafting one, short and sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  弗兰克  但我必须得问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forgive me, Frank, but you know I have to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.36,0:10:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是真的  我会告诉你的  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If it were true, I would tell you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,需要我发表公开声明吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would you like me to go on record?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.87,0:10:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,说我支持你...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Say I stand beside--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.04,0:10:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不不  我很感激  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no, no. I appreciate that, Mr. President,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但你不该为这种烂事脏了自己的手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but you shouldn't dirty your hands with this sort of garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,如果媒体逼问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If the press corners you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他们你不会搬弄是非\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just tell them you don't engage in gossip mongering.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  嘉乐威先生好像要上电视了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, it seems Mr. Galloway is about to appear on television.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧  有需要就告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go. Let me know if there's anything I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.89,0:10:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,下午好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我没什么好说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have very little to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.75,0:10:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一点  我从没和克莱尔·安德伍德有过私情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only that I never had any romantic involvement with Claire Underwood,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,也没有拍摄《特区日报》发表的照片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and that I did not take the photograph printed in the DC Daily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,很遗憾  副总统夫妇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry that the vice president and his wife
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.98,0:10:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,得面对这种荒唐的折磨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}have to go through this ridiculous ordeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我想请媒体不要把我和未婚妻卷入此事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I would ask that the media leave both my fiancée and me out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.19,0:10:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.66,0:10:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,一小时内能准备好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll be ready in an hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  会准备好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. We'll be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,可能得换身更...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You might want to change into something more...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-保守的衣服吗    -对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Conservative?   - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我先放点口风出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna go throw the hounds a bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.08,0:11:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这很丢人...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know it's demeaning --
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.41,0:11:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不用再多说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not another word.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.37,0:11:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我该更谨慎的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should have been more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.79,0:11:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这事就让它过去吧  就像以前一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll put this behind us, just like we've always done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.13,0:11:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我其实也挺希望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Part of me wishes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你会更介意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That you'd be more upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,塔斯克盯上你的原因是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tusk came after you because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你才有资格介意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's you who should be upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.94,0:11:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,浪费精力  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wasted energy, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,对我俩来说都是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,要事先排练一下吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shall we rehearse?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要你的帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是施舍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This ain't a handout.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你得慢慢还给我  给我打工\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have to pay me back over time. Work for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.08,0:12:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,给你打工\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Work for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何  我都会拿到房子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna get the house either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你住不住  那是你的选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whether you choose to live in it is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.94,0:12:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  我就需要这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, just what I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你坐在安乐椅上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You in the easy chair,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,每次我进门出门都对我冷嘲热讽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}laying into me every time I come in and out the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,房子是给你和杜肖恩的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The place is for you and DeShawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.81,0:12:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我住我自己的公寓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna be at my own apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.61,0:12:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定那黑鬼不是在骗你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You sure this nigga ain't just sellin' you smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.61,0:12:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,白纸黑字写在合同里  怎样都有九万五\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Says it right in the contract, 95 Gs no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.53,0:12:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我不确定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,五年没见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Five years I don't see you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.13,0:12:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,现在却跑过来  说你弄到了九万五\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then you come knocking on the door, talking about you got 95 Gs--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.76,0:12:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是你的选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.99,0:12:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你不想再让我去监狱里见你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You didn't want me to visit you no more in jail
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你出来之后也不想见...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you sure didn't want to see me after you got out --
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.25,0:12:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是不想见你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I still don't want to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.47,0:12:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经站在这里了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,滚出去  老家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get the fuck outta here, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.65,0:12:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说  孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You listen to me, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直没什么可以给你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I never had nothing to give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有钱  我有的你也不想要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't have no money, and you didn't want whatever I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但这可是一栋房子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we talking about a house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.30,0:13:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,杜肖恩应该住在一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}DeShawn deserves to live better
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.16,0:13:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-比这里更好的地方    -这不是为了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- than in a place like this.   - This ain't about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.14,0:13:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,而是为了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道去哪里找我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know where to find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.59,0:13:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,再见  孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See you, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,还有不到30分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Less than 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.49,0:13:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要否认吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are they going to deny?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,让副总统和夫人自己来说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna let the Vice President and his wife speak for themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.89,0:13:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他们跟嘉乐威先生有联络吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have they been in contact with Mr. Galloway?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不  没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, they haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么他们过了一整天才做出回应\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why has it taken them a full day to respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.50,0:13:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你们肯定可以理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sure you can understand that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.94,0:13:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想先就诽谤与污蔑问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they wanted to consult with legal counsel first
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.76,0:13:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,咨询法律顾问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}regarding defamation and slander.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.03,0:13:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说他们要否认这段婚外情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're saying they will deny the affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.09,0:13:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说他们30分钟之内就会出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm saying they'll be out here in 30 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.76,0:13:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你们可以引述他们的话而不是我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you can quote them instead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.78,0:13:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们的耐心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you all very much for your patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.57,0:13:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,真是恨死这个了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hate this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,什么  等待吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What, waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不  婚外情  都是狗屁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, the affair. It's bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.58,0:13:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得自己就像个小报狗仔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I feel like a tabloid hack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你宁愿整天被困在白宫那边吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'd rather be stuck at the White House all day?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.77,0:13:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,去他的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.25,0:13:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.97,0:13:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,用我的宝贵时间做点有意义的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To do something meaningful with my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  帮我订一张飞往圣路易斯的机票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, I need you to book me a flight to St. Louis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.52,0:14:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,如果可以的话最好是今晚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tonight, if you can find something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.42,0:14:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,没有问答环节  别费心提问了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No Q&A, so don't even try.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,请大家规矩一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Behave yourselves, people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.36,0:14:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然有人怀疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I find it very painful
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我对我深爱的丈夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that anyone would suggest
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,会有不忠行为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm capable of being unfaithful to my husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这让我感到非常痛心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}whom I love dearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我与亚当·嘉乐威已相识多年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've known Adam Galloway for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都认识他很多年了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We both have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.22,0:14:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我负责净水计划时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I ran the Clean Water Initiative,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,曾委托他为营销活动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I commissioned him to do a series of photographs
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,0:14:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,拍摄了一系列摄影作品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for the marketing campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.79,0:14:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,而他也极为慷慨地为我们的筹款拍卖会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he was extremely generous by donating work
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.04,0:14:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,捐赠了自己的作品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for our fund-raising auctions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我不知道他为什么要否认拍摄过这张照片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So I'm not sure why he would deny taking the photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.63,0:15:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢亚当的作品  所以让他拍了这幅肖像\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I love Adam's work, so I asked him to take this portrait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.34,0:15:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在这里拍的  就在这栋房子里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We did it here, at the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.44,0:15:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,拍摄时弗兰西斯就在旁边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Francis was there during the shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.52,0:15:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一份生日礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was a birthday present.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,克莱尔问我想要什么样的肖像\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Claire asked me what sort of portrait I wanted,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我说就拍她睡着的样子吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I said I want one of her sleeping,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,因为她睡着的时候非常美\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because she's so very beautiful when she's sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,照片就挂在我二楼的办公室里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It hangs in my office on the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在说谎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're fucking lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我只能猜测\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So I can only assume
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,亚当被媒体的关注吓到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that Adam was intimidated by the media attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.76,0:15:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}婚外情传闻: 副总统与夫人出面回应
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,所以想撇清关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and he needed to distance himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.09,0:15:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.56,0:15:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但真相其实就是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But really, all we have here
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.75,0:15:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他是一位才华横溢的摄影师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is a very talented photographer
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,而这是一幅我们很喜爱的作品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and a prized possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you all very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.22,0:15:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,因为那样看上去就太清白了  好像我们...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because it would've seemed too clean otherwise, like we were--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我丢尽了脸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You made me look like an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.80,0:15:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们说法一致\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we had the same story,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.66,0:15:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,媒体会认为我们是串通好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the media would assume we were coordinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.65,0:15:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,必须乱一些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It needed to look messier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这事本该结束的  克莱尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This was supposed to go away, Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在我楼外的记者多了一倍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've got twice as much press outside the building now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.48,0:15:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,亚当\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Adam...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.68,0:15:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我不得不把灯都关上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've gotta keep the lights off
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.69,0:16:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他们在对面楼顶上  想要拍我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'cause they're on the roof across the street, trying to film us inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你只需要证实照片是你为我们拍摄的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You just need to confirm that you took the photo for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,证实我们的说法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Confirm our version.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.33,0:16:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,说你说谎是因为你害怕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Say you lied because you were scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白你为什么不事先\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know why you didn't just tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,把你要做的告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this is what you were intending to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我了解你  你会拒绝的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I know you, and you would've refused.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你自尊心太强了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have too much pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.36,0:16:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想再面对媒体了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want to speak to the press again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,听着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你什么都不说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you say nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不会放过你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they're not going to leave you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会在外面守上几星期\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They will just camp out for weeks on end--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这...我觉得这样不对  克莱尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is... it feels wrong, Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It feels...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.94,0:16:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉我说谎了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry I lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.62,0:16:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不是想摆布你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wasn't trying to be manipulative--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我要挂了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,亚当\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Adam?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,亚当\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Adam?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.75,0:16:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得他会想通的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think he'll do the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不清楚  但愿吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know. I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.85,0:16:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,要来支烟吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了  我去睡了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I'm gonna turn in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.26,0:16:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他上电视了叫我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wake me if he goes on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.64,0:17:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-先生    -道格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Sir.   - Doug,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.49,0:17:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你和赛斯过来一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}why don't you and Seth come over?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.39,0:17:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要考虑起诉这家报纸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Should we consider a lawsuit against the paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.75,0:17:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,表明我们不容忍这种八卦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Show we won't tolerate this sort of gossip?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.05,0:17:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不会和解的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They won't settle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他们乐意上法庭  这样能制造更多新闻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They'll fight it in the courts because it'll generate more news.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.67,0:17:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,总统那儿呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what about the president?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.65,0:17:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他提出要表个态\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He offered to say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这样热度就更高了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Draws more attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.89,0:17:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,总统发话不是个坏主意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}President isn't a bad idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我们帮他起草讲话稿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if we phrase a statement for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.62,0:17:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他成了头条新闻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He becomes the headline
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.67,0:17:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们控制不了他的媒体策略\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and we can't control his press operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果我们和他们协调好  就不会...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if we coordinate with them, it shouldn't --
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.64,0:17:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,协调会让人生疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Coordination looks bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.83,0:17:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你得让人看不出痕迹啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So it's your job to conceal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,如果赛斯觉得总统的讲话有弊无利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If Seth doesn't think the president should make a comment,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就相信他的判断吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then we should defer to his judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我再去拿瓶啤酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna go get another beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.27,0:17:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我帮你去拿吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can go grab you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不用  我正想活动下手脚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I feel like stretching my legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.45,0:17:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,道格  来杯健怡可乐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doug, diet Coke?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.51,0:17:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了  谢谢  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm fine, thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.38,0:17:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,赛斯  来瓶啤酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seth, a beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我还得开车  谢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have to drive, but thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我去去就回\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.60,0:17:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我小心点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Watch yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.98,0:18:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,康纳很容易扳倒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Connor was an easy target,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.65,0:18:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但我可不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.20,0:18:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,道格  能有这位置我已经很满意了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, doug, I'm grateful just to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.03,0:18:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我在副总统身边这么久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think I've survived with the vice president
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.93,0:18:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你这点小花招还看不出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so long by being blind?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.96,0:18:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,给他们工作的晋升空间是有上限的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Upward mobility has a ceiling with the Underwoods.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.81,0:18:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是上限\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm the ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,懂了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你手里还有他们什么把柄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What else have you got on them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,没了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.55,0:18:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你交出日记的时候没留一手吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You fork over the journal without a backup plan for a rainy day?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我不相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.21,0:18:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我有什么牌就出什么牌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had one hand and I played it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会冒险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't press my luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会指望我会相信吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't expect me to believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我没指望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.41,0:18:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,换做我是你我也不相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wouldn't if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但我说的是实话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I'm telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟间的小斗争不是什么坏事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A little sibling rivalry isn't such a bad thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.98,0:18:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,特别是在养子之间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}especially between adopted boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.99,0:18:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要么彼此施压\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They either push each other
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.03,0:18:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,两人都更上一层楼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to be the best versions of themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,要么其中一人被踢回孤儿院\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or one of them gets booted back to the orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.72,0:18:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,在我家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're in my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.66,0:18:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我喝你们也得喝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You drink if I drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你的健怡可乐  你的啤酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One Diet Coke for you, and one beer for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:18:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.58,0:19:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的  真是一团糟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, darling, what a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.96,0:19:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你们还撑得住吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How are you holding up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,媒体接连骚扰了我们两天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The press have been harassing us the past two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们好不容易离开公寓  差点被他们踩死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we barely made it out of the building without being trampled.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.57,0:19:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,太可怕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, how awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你说这儿有人要见我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said someone was here to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.51,0:19:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他在我办公室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's in my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.52,0:19:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他告诉你他是谁了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did he tell you who he was?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想在电话里说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't want to say over the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这世道什么都说不准\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You never know, these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他说他以前为安德伍德夫妇工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He says he used to work for the Underwoods.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.82,0:19:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-是谁    -你的助理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Who?   - Your assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.75,0:19:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-不  她不会...    -她会  她做了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, she would never--   - She would and she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什么目的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的老板\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The man I work for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.47,0:19:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.23,0:19:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这与你无关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That doesn't concern you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.25,0:19:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在搅和我的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is my life you're fucking with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我都只是小卒  嘉乐威先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You and I are just pawns, Mr. Galloway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.11,0:19:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要更多信息...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need more...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.97,0:19:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,来证明这事发生过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...to prove the affair happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,另一张照片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Another photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,给你30秒  走出这扇门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thirty seconds, you better be out the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.81,0:19:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我哪也不去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.98,0:19:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,认识这个国家区号吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You recognize the country code?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,城市区号是波哥大的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the city code is Bogotá.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.41,0:20:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,还没人接听吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it still ringing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,马歇尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Marshall!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.51,0:20:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,老爹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,老天  从没见这里这么火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Man, never seen it like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.59,0:20:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,队都排到街上了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The line's down the block.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,挺壮观  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something else, ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.86,0:20:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你需要人帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Looks like you could use some help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.09,0:20:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,后厨还有条围裙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Got a extra apron in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.40,0:20:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,干活儿了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.16,0:20:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,她赖在门厅不肯走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She refuses to leave the lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.48,0:20:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,她叫什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.74,0:20:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,艾拉·萨伊德  《华尔街电讯报》的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ayla Sayyad, Wall Street Telegraph.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.75,0:20:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,她是副总统的记者团成员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's part of the Vice President's press corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.95,0:20:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,叫她上来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Send her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.95,0:21:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢你了  特莉莎  我没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I appreciate it, tricia, but I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这件事闹个一两天也就过去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This whole thing will blow over in a day or so,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.40,0:21:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那时我再\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.25,0:21:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你能稍等下吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you hold on one second?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,《日报》来电  他们要你发表评论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Daily. They called for a comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.17,0:21:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,亚当和他们谈过了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did Adam speak with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,谈过了  但不是按我们的要求说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, but not what we told him to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他把这个发给报社了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He sent them this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.73,0:21:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,特莉莎  我能过会儿再打给你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tricia, can I call you back?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.95,0:21:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-这是你吗    -不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Is that you?   - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.99,0:21:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但他说这就是你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because he's saying it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.04,0:21:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-可能是    -安德伍德夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It might be.   - Mrs. Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,有可能是  没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, it could be, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.36,0:21:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It probably is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.35,0:21:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我特地问过你还有没有别的把柄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I asked you about any vulnerabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.47,0:21:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道他拍了这张\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't know he took this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,照片里你留着短发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have short hair in the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.09,0:21:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你说过恋情两年前就断了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said it ended over two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.31,0:21:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我去年秋天去过他那儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I visited him last fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.29,0:21:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,还有别人知道吗  有谁在那儿见到过你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does anyone else know? Did anyone see you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他请朋友去过他的公寓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He had friends over, to his apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.27,0:21:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.44,0:21:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们说过他是位朋友了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we've said that he's a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.19,0:22:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我去拜访他  参加聚会没什么问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's nothing wrong with me visiting him, being at a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.30,0:22:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,等这照片上了《日报》的头版就有问题了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is if this photo is on the front page of the Daily.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.14,0:22:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,在中国  政治和生意是纠缠不清的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Politics and business are intertwined in China,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.98,0:22:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,想必你知道这一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as I'm sure you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.41,0:22:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,为了确保中央政府的许可\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not uncommon to partner
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.38,0:22:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,结交有门路的合作伙伴很正常\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with someone who can ensure Beijing's approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.94,0:22:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说你需要他的政治影响力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you needed his political influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.81,0:22:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,费尽心机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All this is moot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.11,0:22:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的合作还是泡汤了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our venture fell through.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.87,0:22:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就在杰斐逊港大桥获批之后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right after the Port Jefferson Bridge was approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.97,0:22:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我和那项工程没有任何关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had nothing to do with that project.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.31,0:22:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,据我所知  冯也没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Neither did Feng, to my knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.14,0:22:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是没有  但是吴彬阳投了资\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, but Wu Bin Yang did.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.49,0:22:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他是冯在北京的主要竞争对手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's Feng's biggest rival in Beijing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.67,0:22:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,看来我没资格给你上中国政治课了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It looks like I shouldn't be schooling you on Chinese politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.76,0:22:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你比我了解的多啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know far more than I.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.32,0:22:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你用了"纠缠不清"这个词\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You used the word "Intertwined."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.34,0:22:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这正是我对整件事的感受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's the sense I'm getting from all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.14,0:22:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,核能补贴  中国精炼厂  大桥工程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The samarium subsidy, the Chinese refinery, the bridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.07,0:22:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,以及你和总统的关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}your friendship with the President...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.25,0:22:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,谁派你来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who sent you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.94,0:22:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,什么派我来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who sent me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.44,0:22:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,财富积累到我这种程度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When you're as rich as I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.72,0:23:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,就总得提防明枪暗箭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you're always a target.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.72,0:23:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己找来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nobody sent me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.33,0:23:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你坐在这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.30,0:23:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,在圣路易斯采访\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in St. Louis.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.74,0:23:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是去报道副总统夫妇的丑闻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Instead of covering the vice president and his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.95,0:23:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得冯山德背后还有更多隐情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My gut says there's more to Xander Feng than has been reported.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.98,0:23:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-是吗    -把时间花在这上面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah.   - It's a far better use of my time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.62,0:23:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,比报道什么八卦性丑闻更值得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}than reporting on tabloid sex scandals.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.03,0:23:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是真正的新闻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not real news.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.40,0:23:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你怀念德黑兰了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You miss Tehran.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.40,0:23:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你在下面等待时  我读了几篇你的文章\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I read some of your work while you were in the waiting area.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.06,0:23:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-那里越来越危险了    -可不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It started to get too dangerous.   - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.73,0:23:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那种环境不适合\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not the best place to be
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.72,0:23:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,结婚成家  生儿育女\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when you want to get married and start a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.97,0:23:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,或者犹太人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or if you're Jewish.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.01,0:23:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,也对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.37,0:23:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我太太去那儿旅游时给我买了这个回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My wife got this for me when she visited there,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.08,0:23:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那是在伊斯兰革命之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}before the revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.01,0:23:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,很漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.66,0:23:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,16世纪的古董\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}16th century.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.58,0:23:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,托运回国的时候被弄碎了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It, um, broke when it was being shipped,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.29,0:23:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,摔得粉碎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}into a thousand pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.61,0:24:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好几名专家花了一年多才修复如初\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It took specialists over a year to restore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.98,0:24:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,给  我希望你能收下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here, I want you to have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.20,0:24:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能接受你的礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't accept gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.65,0:24:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不不  这不是礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no. Not as a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.12,0:24:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,只是给你提个醒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. As a reminder of how hard it can be to
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.65,0:24:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,有些东西一旦碎了  再拼起来就难了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}put something back together again once it's been crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.04,0:24:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是想威胁我的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you're going to threaten me,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.01,0:24:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不用这么兜圈子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you don't have to go to the trouble of veiling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.15,0:24:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我一般不接受记者采访\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't usually do interviews with reporters.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.35,0:24:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就是寄生虫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're parasites.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.99,0:24:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,大都一心琢磨怎么想办法打击我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Usually interested in just finding a way to knock me down a peg.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.98,0:24:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,自然而然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Invariably,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.81,0:24:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他们写的东西都不准确\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}what they write is inaccurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.78,0:24:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们不如实写\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And when that happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.74,0:24:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我就不得不反击了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have no choice but to retaliate.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.98,0:24:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,美国也可以像伊朗一样危险  萨伊德小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}America can be just as dangerous as Iran, ms. Sayyad.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.92,0:24:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你抽时间见我  塔斯克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you for your time, mr. Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.77,0:25:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,回华盛顿的路上注意安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Travel safe back to Washington.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.38,0:25:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,给雷米打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get Remy on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.33,0:25:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,雷米在二线\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Remy's on line two.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.22,0:25:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,雷米\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.24,0:25:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不要再留后手了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's not hold back on the other thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.30,0:25:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,再次打击他  现在就执行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hit 'em again, and hit 'em now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.19,0:25:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,收益最好的一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Best day yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.55,0:25:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你得弄个保险箱什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You gotta get a safe or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.79,0:25:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,或者让银行上门收存款什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or maybe one of those, uh, pickup services.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.48,0:25:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上带这么多钱走路太危险了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's too much money to be carrying around at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.38,0:25:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己能应付\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can handle myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.85,0:25:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你对着枪口还怎么应付\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There ain't nobody can handle a Glock to the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.74,0:25:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你自己有一把\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unless you got one yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.29,0:25:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我早就不带家伙了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My days of packin' are long gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.47,0:25:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,来  拿我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There. Take mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.73,0:25:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我家里还有一把\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got one at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.19,0:25:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你把那东西带到这里来干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What the fuck you doin' bringin' that thing in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.88,0:25:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,只是为了安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, it's just for protection, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.82,0:26:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不知道你为什么要有枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know what you doing with it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.94,0:26:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你的假释条例怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about your parole?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.22,0:26:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,比起假释官我更担心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm a lot more worried about niggas in my building
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.05,0:26:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我家楼里的黑鬼们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}than some parole officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.90,0:26:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  坐下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.79,0:26:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你瞧  我说的就是这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See, man? This is what I'm talkin' about, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.28,0:26:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你自以为是地评价我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You being all righteous and judgin' me and shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.05,0:26:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,给我个面子  坐下  现在坐下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do me a favor and just sit down. Sit down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.69,0:26:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,听着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.40,0:26:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可能遇到件好事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We got us a good thing, potentially.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.19,0:26:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,可能最终没有结果  也可能会有好结果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe nothing comes of it, but maybe something does.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.30,0:26:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,如果连锁店成功\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If the joint works out,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.02,0:26:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,或许有一天你能当经理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}maybe one day you could be the manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.76,0:26:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,如果真的火起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shit, if it blows up,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.03,0:26:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你能去经营整个连锁店\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you could run the whole fucking franchise.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.32,0:26:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但那意味着你得小心点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But that means you gotta be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.31,0:26:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能再被抓回去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That means you cannot be sent back inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.76,0:26:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得遵纪守法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We gotta follow the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.22,0:26:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,听懂了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.03,0:26:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.81,0:27:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你会处理掉那东西吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You gonna get rid of that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.82,0:27:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.67,0:27:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.76,0:27:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这才像个男人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now that's what's being a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.98,0:27:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你剪短头发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll need you to cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.82,0:27:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,多短\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How short?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.40,0:27:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这么短\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This short.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.72,0:27:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我还要做模特呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have a modeling career.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.07,0:27:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我剪那么短\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I cut it that short--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.97,0:27:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你真有模特工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you actually had a modeling career,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.90,0:27:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我就会在和你经纪人谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would be speaking to your agency,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.52,0:27:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是坐在你的公寓里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and not sitting in your apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.73,0:27:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底想不想要这份工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you want this job or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.46,0:27:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}OK, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.98,0:27:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以剪短\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.15,0:27:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.11,0:27:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们去摄影棚之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And before we go to the studio,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.67,0:27:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要知道你是否口齿清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need to see how well-spoken you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.63,0:27:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这有什么关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why does that matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.68,0:27:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你会出现在全美所有的新闻频道上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because you're gonna be on every news channel in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.86,0:27:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  这是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait. What's this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.60,0:27:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,读出这个  一字不差\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Read this. Those exact words.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.66,0:28:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,读出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Read 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.38,0:28:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你有本事  就该背出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you're good, you'll memorize them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.01,0:28:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我的名字是斯特芬妮·道瑞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My name is Stephanie Daldry.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.49,0:28:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我是一个职业模特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am a professional model.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.79,0:28:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,弗莱迪·海耶斯因在哥伦比亚高地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Freddy Hayes was convicted in 1982
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.14,0:28:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,抢劫一家便利店  而于1982年被定罪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for sticking up a convenience store in Columbia Heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.59,0:28:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,在高速追捕中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}During a high-speed pursuit,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.91,0:28:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,海耶斯失控撞向另一辆车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hayes lost control and crashed into another vehicle,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.92,0:28:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,导致一对老夫妇死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}killing an elderly couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.09,0:28:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他对持械抢劫认罪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He avoided manslaughter charges
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.56,0:28:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,以免受过失杀人的起诉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by pleading guilty to armed robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.94,0:28:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他服刑九年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He served nine years.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.37,0:28:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,1992年他开了弗莱迪烧烤餐馆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In 1992 he opened Freddy's BBQ Joint,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.28,0:28:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,一家专做肋排的小餐馆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a small restaurant specializing in ribs,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.34,0:28:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,副总统弗兰克·安德伍德是那里的常客\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}frequented by Vice President Frank Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.70,0:28:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.39,0:28:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.20,0:28:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为是塔斯克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think it's Tusk?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.28,0:28:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,还能是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who else?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.00,0:29:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}弗·安德伍德至赛斯·格雷森  你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.48,0:28:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你在给谁发短信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who are you texting?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.45,0:28:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,赛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seth.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.20,0:29:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}赛斯·格雷森  摄影棚
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.40,0:29:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}弗·安德伍德  来我家
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.77,0:29:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我想发布一份简短声明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All I want to do is make a short statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.14,0:29:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,弗莱迪已经服过刑了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Freddy did his time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.75,0:29:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他20年来一直遵纪守法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's been an upstanding citizen for 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.93,0:29:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个杀死两位老人的重罪犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's a convicted felon who killed two senior citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.56,0:29:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是意外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.71,0:29:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那并不是重点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that's beside the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.61,0:29:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能不管他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am not gonna hang him out to dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.50,0:29:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,如果没有嘉乐威的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If the Galloway story wasn't happening,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.19,0:29:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为这可以\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd say it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.55,0:29:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在太冒险了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it's too risky right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.53,0:29:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,想想这看起来像什么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Think of how this is shaping up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.12,0:29:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,一个戴绿帽子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A vice president whose wife cheats on him
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.87,0:29:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,还和前罪犯做朋友的副总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and who is friendly with a former gang-banger?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.95,0:29:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你维护他不会有好结果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is no way you win standing up for this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.15,0:29:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他马上要开连锁店了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's about to start a franchise.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.71,0:29:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我不容许这事告吹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will not have it jeopardized
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.99,0:29:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,就因为塔斯克决定针对...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because Tusk decides to come after --
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.67,0:29:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这不单是弗莱迪的问题  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is more than just Freddy, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.13,0:29:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我做过调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did some digging.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.66,0:29:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他儿子因运毒和贩毒坐过牢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His son did time for narcotics, trafficking, distribution--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.47,0:29:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我没见过他儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've never met his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.71,0:29:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这件事再缓缓  先解决\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's hold off and tackle--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.06,0:29:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不  明早安排我跟记者见一下面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I want you to organize a press avail tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.57,0:29:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,派人接弗莱迪过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have Freddy brought over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.53,0:29:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,从后门进\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bring him through the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.27,0:29:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.10,0:30:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会对自己人见死不救\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I won't leave one of my own bleeding on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.98,0:30:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是华盛顿红人队\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you're gonna have the Washington Redskins,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.90,0:30:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那对手必须是纽约尼克斯队\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then you're gonna have to have the New York Knickers.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.90,0:30:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}华盛顿红人是美式足球队  纽约尼克斯是篮球队
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.59,0:30:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸  你完全弄错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pops, you ain't even deep like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.85,0:30:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,走开  伙计\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yo, back off, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.45,0:30:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,都他妈滚开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Back the fuck off.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.51,0:30:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,达奈尔  别理他们就好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Darnell, just ignore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.38,0:30:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你当我在开玩笑吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think I'm fucking around?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.49,0:30:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,达奈尔  别理他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Darnell, ignore them! Ignore 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.28,0:30:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不想被拍  他们就不能拍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They can't take our pictures if we don't want them to.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.34,0:30:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,老子当然能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sure as hell can.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.79,0:30:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.69,0:30:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}美国宪法第一修正案保护新闻自由
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.69,0:30:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,第一修正案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The First fuckin' Amendment.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.61,0:30:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈要给我讲宪法吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You gonna read me the constitution now, motherfucker?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.72,0:30:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,行了  达奈尔  我们进去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, Darnell. Let's just go on inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.61,0:30:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不行  我和这混蛋还没完\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nah, nah, I ain't done with this asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.85,0:30:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,别碰我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, don't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.17,0:30:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你能威胁我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you can get all up in my face
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.49,0:30:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我却不能威胁你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I can't get up in yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.65,0:30:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,听你老爸的话  冷静点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen to your daddy and chill out.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.21,0:30:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,达奈尔  我们走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Darnell, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.15,0:30:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,别逼我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't push me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.12,0:30:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,小心我揍你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will fuck you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.38,0:30:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为我怕你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think I'm scared of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.52,0:30:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,怕这个吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You scared of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.53,0:30:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,达奈尔  你的保释\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Darnell! Parole!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.42,0:30:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,能告诉我你的名字吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you tell me your name, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.02,0:30:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,斯特芬妮·道瑞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stephanie Daldry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.33,0:30:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我是一名职业模特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm a professional model.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.15,0:30:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,右边照片里的人是你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And this is you in this photo on the right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.21,0:31:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}安德伍德照片真实性遭质疑
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.06,0:30:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, that's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.26,0:31:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,道瑞小姐的这张照是昨天拍的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We shot this photo yesterday with Ms. Daldry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.99,0:31:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说嘉乐威先生的照片是假的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you're suggesting that Mr. Galloway's photo is a fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.50,0:31:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我对专业摄影一无所知\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know anything about professional photography,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.27,0:31:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}赛斯·格雷森  副总统新闻发言人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.88,0:31:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是个做宣传的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just a flack.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.84,0:31:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果我们都能在24小时内伪造照片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if we can create a fake in less than 24 hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.36,0:31:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,像亚当·嘉乐威那样的专业摄影师...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think an expert photographer like Adam Galloway--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.42,0:31:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这指控相当严重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those are serious allegations,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.78,0:31:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,特别是在嘉乐威先生极力否认的情况下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}especially given that Mr. Galloway vehemently denies it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.35,0:31:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我对他的否认并不意外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not surprised he's denying.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.25,0:31:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不过最后就是你们两人对质了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ultimately, though, it's gonna be your word against his.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.80,0:31:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.40,0:31:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是美国的副总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The vice president of the United States'.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.86,0:31:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他和一个可能有问题的人的对质\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's his word versus that of a potentially troubled man.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.58,0:31:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,有问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Troubled?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.57,0:31:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Potentially.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.45,0:31:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,或许他是有动机的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or maybe he has a motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.37,0:31:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嘉乐威先生会有什么造假的动机呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What motive could Mr. Galloway possibly have for a fake photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.48,0:31:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他能从中得到什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What would he get out of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.95,0:31:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.52,0:31:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我的工作是区分事实和虚构\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My job is to separate fact from fiction,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.67,0:31:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这点和你一样  坎迪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just like yours is, Candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.66,0:31:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但或许对搞艺术的人来说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But maybe fact and fiction
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.55,0:31:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,事实和虚构不那么重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}don't matter as much to the artistic sensibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.99,0:31:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,或许他分得不那么清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe the lines are blurred for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.70,0:31:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他并不拍摄虚构的作品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is not a man who stages fictitious scenarios.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.29,0:31:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才也说了  我不懂艺术\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like I said, the art stuff, it's over my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.12,0:31:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,或许你是对的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.13,0:31:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不愿相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I would hate to think
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.30,0:32:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嘉乐威先生这么做仅仅是为了炒作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that Mr. Galloway was doing this just for publicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.38,0:32:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为这是炒作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think it's a publicity stunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.82,0:32:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,进来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.35,0:32:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.99,0:32:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,弗莱迪在路上了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is Freddy on his way?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.61,0:32:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他儿子出事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There was an incident with his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.08,0:32:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.00,0:32:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他因持枪威胁摄像师被警方拘留\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's in custody for threatening a photographer with a firearm.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.19,0:32:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.49,0:32:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,弗莱迪现在在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is Freddy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.64,0:32:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他在家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.89,0:32:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我得去看他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have to go see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.42,0:32:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那里是贫困住宅区\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's the projects, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.29,0:32:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我不管  你看着办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't care, you figure it out,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.75,0:32:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,而且不能让媒体知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the press can't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.73,0:32:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.95,0:32:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰西斯  我也很喜欢弗莱迪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Francis, you know I love Freddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.93,0:32:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定要去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.92,0:32:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,弗莱迪很危险  因为你太在乎了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Freddy is dangerous because you care too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.29,0:32:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,太过在乎  会使人盲目\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When we care too much, it blinds us.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.08,0:32:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,塔斯克的做法太卑鄙了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What Tusk did is cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.06,0:32:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但你却让这事影响到你  这正是他的目的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you're letting it get to you, which is exactly what he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.59,0:32:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我视而不见  无所作为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I ignore this, if I do nothing--
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.82,0:32:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是无所作为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.62,0:32:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,保持专注也需要力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Staying focused requires strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.90,0:32:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,要我给你做点什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want me to make something?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.79,0:32:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你吃吧  我不饿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You go ahead. I'm not hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.75,0:33:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你得吃点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.74,0:33:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  这本来跟你无关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry. You didn't ask for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.77,0:33:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这对你不公平\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not fair to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.67,0:33:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想快点结束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All I want is to be done with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.96,0:33:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,让我父亲平安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For my father to be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.39,0:33:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我当时还有别的办法...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I thought there was any other way, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.27,0:33:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想冒险让他...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't want to take the chance that he would--
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.81,0:33:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.88,0:33:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These people.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.50,0:33:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我一向知道他们很无情  但是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I always knew they were ruthless, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.80,0:33:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们像动物一样关在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're caged up in here like animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.78,0:33:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他们把我刻画成了那种...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're painting me as some sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.47,0:33:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你的家人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And your family...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.09,0:33:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,太残忍了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's inhuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.83,0:33:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他们太他妈残忍了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're fucking inhuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.45,0:33:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,生气也不能改变局面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Getting worked up isn't going to change anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.66,0:33:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.15,0:33:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.89,0:34:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.77,0:34:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,可以了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.63,0:34:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你来看我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks for dropping by.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.54,0:34:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How you holdin' up?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.89,0:34:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I been better.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.52,0:34:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,从没见过你不穿西装的样子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ain't never seen you without a suit before.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.15,0:34:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不想太招人注意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We didn't want to draw too much attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.96,0:34:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样  我的城堡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, this is it, my castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.99,0:34:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不如你的大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ain't as big as yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.08,0:34:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但也够用了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it'll do the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.61,0:34:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,盲眼威利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Blind Willie.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.80,0:34:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}盲眼威利·约翰逊: 美国福音蓝调歌手  吉他演奏家
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.56,0:34:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢蓝调吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you a blues fan?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.21,0:34:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,《漆黑的夜晚》\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Dark Was the Night."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.18,0:34:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,每次听都让我陶醉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gets me every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.93,0:34:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计  你早该告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Man, you shoulda told me that years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.84,0:34:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我会即兴演奏  聊起蓝调能聊一整天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can jam, talking about some blues all day long.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.58,0:34:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,看看这张  78年原版\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Check this out. Original 78.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.62,0:34:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,要喝点什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want something?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.65,0:35:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,水  还是冰茶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Water? Iced tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.14,0:35:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要冰茶  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd like some iced tea, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.73,0:35:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你儿子怎么样了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How's your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.14,0:35:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要六万保释金\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They set the bail at 60 grand.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.79,0:35:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.03,0:35:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你妻子怎么样了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How's your wife doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.69,0:35:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,克莱尔有一副三英寸厚的铠甲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, Claire's got a suit of armor three inches thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.60,0:35:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这些难关我们会撑过去的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll get through all this garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.33,0:35:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,有人想毁了你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Somebody's tryin' to take you out?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.06,0:35:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,看来是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Appears that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.92,0:35:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,无论是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whoever it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.82,0:35:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他们踩到不该踩的响尾蛇了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they done stepped on the wrong motherfuckin' rattlesnake.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.97,0:35:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我来这里了  弗莱迪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's why I'm here, Freddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.95,0:35:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我得远离你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have to distance myself from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.97,0:35:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我要确保你不会到处宣扬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need to make sure you're not going to play up
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.05,0:35:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是多好的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}what good friends we've been.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.07,0:35:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,说你去过我的办公室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That you've been to my office,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.86,0:35:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,还曾在我家做晚餐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that you've cooked dinner at my home,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.05,0:35:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,而且总统也出席了那次晚餐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or that the president was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.10,0:36:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能连累了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't drag him into anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.43,0:36:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我再也不会来吃肋排了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I won't be coming in for ribs anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.19,0:36:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,现在出了这么多事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With all that's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.29,0:36:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能再火上浇油了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we can't add fuel to the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.33,0:36:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是想来吃也吃不到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You couldn't if you wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.08,0:36:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我要卖掉了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm selling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.51,0:36:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,卖掉餐馆吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Selling the Joint?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.73,0:36:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.54,0:36:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.58,0:36:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,酱汁的特许经营权什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The franchise thing, with the sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.77,0:36:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我的生意伙伴要解约了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My business partner's pullin' out.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.18,0:36:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,说他们银泉的白人不喜欢去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Say them white folks down in Silver Spring don't wanna
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.80,0:36:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,恶棍开的餐馆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}go to no place run by thugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.15,0:36:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那你为什么非得卖掉你的店\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why do you have to sell yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.82,0:36:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,达奈尔的保释金\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Darnell's bail.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.27,0:36:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙不是无论如何都得给你十万美金吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doesn't that guy have to give you a hundred grand, regardless?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.05,0:36:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我屁都拿不到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I ain't getting shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.59,0:36:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,合同里有一条道德条款\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a morality clause in the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.73,0:36:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但他打算花四万五买我的门面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But he's gonna pay me 45 thou for the storefront.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.60,0:36:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那再加上我存的一点钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That with what little I got saved,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.04,0:36:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就可以付保释金了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can pay that bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.37,0:36:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能把餐馆卖掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't sell Freddy's.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.85,0:36:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他已经在起草合同了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's already drawing up the papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.69,0:36:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我来帮你解决钱的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me help you with the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.16,0:36:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不用  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nah, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.77,0:36:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,就当做是借贷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll make it a loan.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.57,0:37:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以以后再还我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can pay me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.52,0:37:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.24,0:37:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,别要强\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't be prideful.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.05,0:37:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-弗兰克    -拜托  让我帮你吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Frank.   - Please, let me help.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.47,0:37:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是内疚  我不会要的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I ain't takin' your guilt money.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.67,0:37:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,过去在道上的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I was bangin',
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.51,0:37:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一个月能赚六万美金\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we used to clear 60 Gs a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.26,0:37:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我见过同伴被人残忍枪杀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I seen guys shot down execution-style.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.86,0:37:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但我一点也不关心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't give a shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.91,0:37:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,之后我被捕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then I got caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.95,0:37:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,坐牢的第一年里达奈尔出生了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Darnell was born my first year in.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.57,0:37:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我一次也没见过他  连照片都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never saw him once, not even a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.01,0:37:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能收回我所犯的罪恶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't take back the bad I done.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.22,0:37:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我所能做的就是一如既往\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All I can do is to make my own way,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.55,0:37:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,过好自己的生活  你明白吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}like I've been doing. You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.94,0:37:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不是要强  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ain't pride, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.02,0:38:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你改变心意了  就告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you change your mind, you let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.43,0:38:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你是一个好顾客  仅此而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You was a good customer, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.94,0:38:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你不必假装是我的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You ain't gotta pretend to be my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.99,0:38:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,多多保重  弗莱迪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You take care of yourself, Freddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.93,0:38:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You too, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.36,0:38:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得我是一个伪君子吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you think I'm a hypocrite?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.88,0:38:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那就对了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you should.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.78,0:38:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会否认\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wouldn't disagree with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.41,0:38:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,通向权利的道路由虚伪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The road to power is paved with hypocrisy...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.81,0:38:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,和牺牲铺就\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...and casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.73,0:38:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,永远不要后悔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.99,0:39:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这边请\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.20,0:39:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,请坐  亚当\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have a seat, Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.58,0:39:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你按要求的那样  把电话留在家里了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You left your phone at home, as you were asked?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.35,0:39:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.91,0:39:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎么跟你未婚妻说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what did you tell your fiancée exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.36,0:39:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,就说我要离开一阵子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That I'd be gone for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.81,0:39:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,她不知道我要去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She doesn't know where.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.07,0:39:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有人找到她  她会说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what will she say if someone checks in on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.97,0:39:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这是干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.66,0:39:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,她会说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What will she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.68,0:39:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰西斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Francis.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.92,0:39:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在得团结协作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to work together now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.53,0:39:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我试过  但你骗了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I tried. You lied to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.31,0:40:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,而我也解释了为什么要那么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I explained to you why that was necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.62,0:40:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,可你不听我的命令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You didn't follow my instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.17,0:40:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你们知道雷米·丹顿是谁吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know who Remy Danton is?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.69,0:40:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他找过你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He approached you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.26,0:40:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,伊奈兹的父亲是波哥大的一位人权运动家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Inez's father is a human rights activist in Bogotá.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.07,0:40:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,政府以叛国的罪名控告他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The government has charged him with treason
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.46,0:40:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,与叛乱分子勾结\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for working with the rebels.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.31,0:40:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要判他死刑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're going for the death penalty,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.53,0:40:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,丹顿说他们可以操纵法官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and Danton said they have the judge in their pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.79,0:40:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该来找我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should have come to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.60,0:40:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟他说了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.47,0:40:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,丹顿说你们什么也做不了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Danton said you couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.76,0:40:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.95,0:40:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能冒险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wasn't gonna take any chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.34,0:40:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,她父亲如政府所称那样犯罪了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Has he done what the government's claiming?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.54,0:40:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,没有  都是些无中生有的指控\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. They're made-up charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.89,0:40:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是一个记者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's a journalist
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.59,0:40:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,报道达恩地堑那里的残暴行径\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}documenting atrocities in the Darien Gap.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.59,0:40:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}巴拿马与哥伦比亚之间未开发的大片沼泽地
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.64,0:40:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以撤销控告\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can get the charges dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.05,0:40:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我凭什么相信你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why should I trust you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.95,0:40:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,因为国务卿是我的好朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because the secretary of state is a good friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.20,0:40:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你别无选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you don't have any other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.94,0:40:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是你的棋子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're not your chess pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.82,0:40:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这也不是游戏  嘉乐威先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And this isn't a game, Mr. Galloway.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.73,0:40:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那你为什么要耍我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then why are you toying with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.84,0:40:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只是想帮你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are trying to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.72,0:40:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑  克莱尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's a fucking joke, Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.04,0:40:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不准这样和我妻子说话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do not talk to my wife that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.50,0:41:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你妻子  那对你来说有什么意义\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your wife. What does that even mean to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.64,0:41:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,别因为你们之间有过一段历史\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do not mistake any history you have shared
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.31,0:41:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就以为你了解我们的婚姻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for the slightest understanding of what our marriage is
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.13,0:41:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,或是相比之下你是多么无关紧要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or how insignificant you are in comparison.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.27,0:41:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,能让我俩单独谈谈吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you give us a few minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.51,0:41:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我去给凯茜打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna go call Cathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.28,0:41:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不说我的工作和名声吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forget my career and my reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.73,0:41:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我想和这个女人结婚  克莱尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to marry this woman, Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.03,0:41:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会摆平这件事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're going to make this disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.92,0:41:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你  我将永远是那个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because of you I will always be the man
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.61,0:41:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,将她父亲置于险境的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who placed her father in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.06,0:41:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这永远无法抹去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can never erase that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.41,0:41:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉事情走到了这个地步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry it's come to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.89,0:41:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我真后悔遇见你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry I ever met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.08,0:41:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,从头到尾  你只给过我痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All you've ever done is cause me pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.31,0:41:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你又来破坏我的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now you're fucking with my life
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.36,0:41:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我未婚妻的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the life of the woman
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.37,0:41:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱她远胜过爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that I love more than I ever loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.79,0:41:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你今晚就开车回纽约\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll be driven back to New York tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.91,0:41:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,明天一早  你就发表声明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the morning, you'll make a statement saying
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.53,0:41:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,说这是炒作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this was a publicity stunt,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.66,0:42:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你的作品一直卖不出好价钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and that the value of your work had been stagnating
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.64,0:42:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你希望重振\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you wanted to revive--
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.45,0:42:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不  克莱尔  我才不会那样做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, Claire. I won't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.66,0:42:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.69,0:42:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不如我去告诉记者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How about I tell the press--
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.38,0:42:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,亚当  闭嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Adam, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.46,0:42:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你要说你想博取关注\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That you wanted the attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.02,0:42:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,然后又害怕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then you got cold feet,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.35,0:42:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,否认了照片的事  接着又再次改了主意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}denied it, then you changed your mind again.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.86,0:42:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那张浴室照片是你伪造的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that you faked the shower photo
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.84,0:42:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你要澄清这一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you're coming clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.26,0:42:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.43,0:42:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想被卷进这些事中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not part of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.87,0:42:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我没想搅进来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't sign up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.80,0:42:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不感兴趣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have no interest in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.75,0:42:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们给你提供了一条出路  亚当\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're giving you an out, Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.21,0:42:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你选择不接受的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if you choose not to take it,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.79,0:42:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我会毁掉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will bury you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.16,0:42:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没恨过任何人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've never hated anyone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.32,0:42:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我知道那是什么感觉了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now I know what that feels like.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.61,0:42:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉很糟  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a terrible feeling, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.24,0:43:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,终止呼叫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}End call.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.57,0:43:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,呼叫已终止\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Call ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.76,0:43:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,呼叫雷蒙德·塔斯克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Call Raymond Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.74,0:43:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他的住处没人接电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No answer at his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.02,0:43:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是想要更多钱吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it a matter of more money?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.94,0:43:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,国务卿杜兰特已经致电莫里诺总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Secretary Durant has already called President Moreno.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.50,0:43:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们得赶快行动了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So we need to move quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.29,0:43:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,外交部长已经牵扯进来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The minister of foreign affairs is involved now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.60,0:43:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,法官不会在12小时内就宣判他有罪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The judge isn't gonna rush a conviction in less than 12 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.66,0:43:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们认识什么能跟部长说上话的人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who do we know who has the minister's ear?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.08,0:43:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人能够比得过莫里诺总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nobody who can trump President Moreno.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.52,0:43:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,而他对杜兰特对人权方面的看法非常敏感\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he's very sensitive to Durant's view on human rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.47,0:43:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你是打算放弃了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you giving up on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.73,0:43:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不  只是现实一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Just being realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.80,0:43:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那就做莫里诺的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Work on Moreno then.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.34,0:43:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们快要被人察觉了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll start leaving footprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.80,0:43:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,安静点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.96,0:43:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.82,0:43:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不是说你  是我的鸟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, not you. My birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.75,0:43:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们要做好准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think we need to be prepared
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.21,0:44:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很可能没法把威胁进行到底了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for the possibility that we can't follow through with our threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.25,0:44:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我听到的都是借口  不是解决方案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am hearing excuses, not solutions.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.94,0:44:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我无能为力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My hands are tied.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.73,0:44:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我没法搞定整个美国国务院\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't circumvent the entire US State Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.23,0:44:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我雇你是为了让你毁掉弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, I hired you to destroy Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.66,0:44:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你要失败了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're failing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.44,0:44:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙德  我是你的说客\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, Raymond, I'm your lobbyist,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.07,0:44:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不是你的走狗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not your henchman.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.87,0:44:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我雇的不是说客\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't employ lobbyists.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.08,0:44:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我雇的是对我有用的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I employ people who can be useful to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.95,0:44:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,而你看起来没用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you are proving otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.08,0:44:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,安静点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Quiet now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.02,0:44:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我会想办法的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll figure something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.53,0:44:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.29,0:44:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,行  就这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.77,0:44:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你不必这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.45,0:44:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我必须这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.63,0:44:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,指控撤销了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The charges are dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.88,0:44:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他们骗了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They lied to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.76,0:44:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你也可以骗他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can lie to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.91,0:44:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,还可以提出新指控\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}New charges can always be filed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.77,0:44:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不能冒这个险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not worth the risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.28,0:44:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.46,0:45:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你对我感到失望吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you disappointed in me?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.34,0:45:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧把这事弄完吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's just get it over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.18,0:45:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}OK, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.27,0:45:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我要做出一项声明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd like to make a statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.38,0:45:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,还需要一些扫尾工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There will be a little cleanup,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.54,0:45:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,会有一些人继续关注这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}some folks who will want to linger on the story,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.12,0:45:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们已经渡过最困难的阶段了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we're over the hump, I'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.40,0:45:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们现在可以出门了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So we can leave the house now?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.21,0:45:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,越快恢复正常工作越好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The sooner you get back to normal work, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.29,0:45:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,之前被迫取消的会议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All the meetings I had to cancel,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.44,0:45:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,想办法再做安排\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}let's find a way to get them back on the books.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.98,0:45:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.59,0:45:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我得继续推动性侵法案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need to push ahead with the Assault Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.56,0:45:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们为您安排了明天和马特·贝的采访\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've got your Matt Bai interview lined up for tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.69,0:45:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但我认为...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I think that--
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.37,0:45:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们应该等事情平息之后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe we should hold off on Bai
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.27,0:45:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,再考虑贝的采访\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}till after things quiet down.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.39,0:45:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚才正打算这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's exactly what I was gonna suggest.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.12,0:45:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,道格说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doug is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.86,0:45:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好  那我们出发吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}OK, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.82,0:45:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我在车里等你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll meet you in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.74,0:45:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他这些事处理得很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's done a good job handling all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.79,0:45:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, he has.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.24,0:45:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们还要担心什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Should we have any more concerns?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.34,0:45:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他说他没有别的把柄了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He claims he doesn't have anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.45,0:45:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你相信他吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you believe him?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.67,0:46:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没到那个地步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wouldn't go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.02,0:46:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,盯着他点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep an eye on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.41,0:46:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,正有此意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I plan to.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.60,0:46:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,至于雷蒙德  我们快速有力地回击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As for Raymond, we have to strike back hard and fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.21,0:46:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我要打垮他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want him obliterated.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.22,0:46:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,还不够\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}More than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.49,0:46:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,让他受点折磨吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's make him suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.39,0:46:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真不知我是该骄傲还是害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know whether to be proud or terrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.66,0:46:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,也许两者皆有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps both.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.07,0:46:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,真希望我能多给你一些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wish I could do more.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.01,0:46:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算拿她做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What you gonna do with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.85,0:46:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,还没想好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.20,0:47:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,也许要把它拆掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Probably have to knock it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.87,0:47:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,空地价值更高\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's worth more as an empty lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.86,0:47:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你还有别的东西想拿走吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is there anything else you wanna take?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.20,0:47:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,纪念品之类的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A memento or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.76,0:47:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,没了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.87,0:47:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是一个向后看的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I ain't one for lookin' back.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.62,0:47:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我只向前看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Eyes ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.02,0:47:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你好运  弗莱迪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good luck, Freddy.
